column2: Shake your left hands in the air 8 times while counting to 8
Do it as fast and loud as you can
Repeat with your other hand. Repeat with each foot.
Do it 7 times, then 6 times and continue until you get to 1.
Everyone calls out “Crazy chicken” and does their best crazy chicken dance!",,,,,,,,,,,,,,,9d2afa2a-503a-4844-a0e1-bc5f48d680cd,,execute_actions,;
